description:
Make your kitty’s gift unforgettable this year with a special holiday-themed Goody Box by Chewy.
This holiday Goody Box includes a penguin plush kicker toy; a pack of 10 bouncy, holiday-colored spring toys; a foldable play tunnel; and delicious treats from Temptations and Hartz Delectables. Plus, all three toys include catnip, for maxed-out holiday excitement.
Each item has been hand-picked by the pet-obsessed experts at Chewy.
Save up to 35% by bundling all these cat-approved products together.
Provides an opportunity to strengthen your bond and make this holiday the best one yet.

100% nutritionally and complete rewards for adult cats.
Each piece has under two calories per treat, so your cat can enjoy more, and you don’t have to feel guilty about giving her more!
Delivers a variety of textures with a crunchy outside and a soft and creamy inside.
Made with a unique pocket shape and a lip-smacking tuna, shrimp and salmon flavors that will have your pal purring for more.
Crafted with vitamins and taurine—an amino acid that helps support your cat’s overall health and well-being.
